*Google Analytics in Real Life*
Ever thought about what it would look like if the keywords we put in Google 
Analytics and on our website were the terms we used in real life? This 
video plays that scenario out and teaches us a couple things: *1) This 
would be **hilarious** ridiculous in real life and 2) We have to remember 
who our browsers are and what they’re looking for.*﻿
